

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html >
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>The Chitrakars: Magic Wand</title>
  
  
  
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/style3.css">

  
</head>

<body>
<h3>PRODUCT EXPLAINER INFORMATION</h3>
<div class="column last"> 

    <iframe src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/203084520" width="640" height="360" frameborder="0" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen align="right"></iframe>

</div>
<div align="left">
<form id="contact-form" action="/prepareObject" method="post" enctype = "multipart/form-data">
  <p>Meet
   <input id="characterName" type="text" class="form-control" name="characterName" 
              pattern="[A-Za-z\s]{2,15}"
              placeholder="Your customer name" value="<%= clientData[0].characterName %>" title="Character Name should be min length of 2 and max length of 10 with A-Za-z" required>
 He's a   <input 
              id="characterProfession" 
              type="text" 
              class="form-control" 
              name="characterProfession" 
              pattern="[A-Za-z\s]{2,20}"
              placeholder="Your customer profession" value="<%= clientData[0].characterProfession %>" 
              title="Character profession should be min length of 2 and max length of 10 with A-Za-z" required></p>
 
  <p><label for="email">He's struggling to </label>
    <input 
              id="problemStatement" 
              type="text" 
              class="form-control" 
              name="problemStatement" 
              pattern="[A-Za-z0-9\s]{2,80}"
              placeholder="problem of your customer " value="<%= clientData[0].problemStatement %>"
              title="Character profession should be min length of 5 and max length of 80 with A-Za-z" required>
  </p>

  <p>He has explored 
    <label for="your-message">every option</label> available</p>
  <p> <input 
              id="exploredOption1" 
              type="text" 
              class="form-control" 
              name="exploredOption1" 
              pattern="[A-Za-z0-9\s]{2,20}"
              placeholder="First option" value="<%= clientData[0].exploredOption1 %>"
              title="Option should be min length of 5 and max length of 20 with A-Za-z" required>
    <input 
              id="exploredOption2" 
              type="text" 
              class="form-control" 
              name="exploredOption2" 
              pattern="[A-Za-z0-9\s]{2,20}"
              placeholder="Second option" value="<%= clientData[0].exploredOption2 %>"
              title="Option should be min length of 2 and max length of 20 with A-Za-z" required>
     <input 
              id="exploredOption3" 
              type="text" 
              class="form-control" 
              name="exploredOption3" 
              pattern="[A-Za-z0-9\s]{2,20}"
              placeholder="Third option"  value="<%= clientData[0].exploredOption3 %>"
              title="Option should be min length of 2 and max length of 10 with A-Za-z" required>
  <p>And lost control on things to focus...</p>
    That is when he heard about  
    <p> <input 
              id="productName" 
              type="text" 
              class="form-control" 
              name="productName" 
              pattern="[A-Za-z0-9\s]{2,20}"
              placeholder="Your product name" value="<%= clientData[0].productName %>"
              title="Product name should be min length of 2 and max length of 20 with A-Za-z" required>  

     Product logo
  <input 
              type="file" 
              class="btn btn-default btn-file col-xs-12"  value="<%= clientData[0].productLogo %>"
              name="productLogo" required >
              </p>
              <p>Product tagline <input 
              id="slogan" 
              type="text" 
              class="form-control" 
              name="slogan" 
              placeholder="Provide your Tagline"  value="<%= clientData[0].slogan %>"
              pattern="[A-Za-z0-9\s]{5,60}"
              title="Slogan should be min length of 5 and max length of 60 with A-Za-z0-9.*&:" required> </p> 
   It solves by  <input 
              id="solutionOffered" 
              type="text" 
              class="form-control" 
              name="solutionOffered" 
              placeholder="Provide the solution offered" value="<%= clientData[0].solutionOffered %>"
              pattern="[A-Za-z0-9\s]{5,60}"
                            title="About should be min length of 5 and max length of 60 with A-Za-z" required>



  <p>Here are the main key features</p>
  <p> <input 
              id="keyFeature1" 
              type="text" 
              class="form-control" 
              name="keyFeature1" 
              placeholder="Provide the first key feature"  value="<%= clientData[0].keyFeature1 %>"
              pattern="[A-Za-z0-9\s]{5,60}"
              title="About should be min length of 5 and max length of 60 with A-Za-z" required>
    
  <input 
              id="keyFeature2" 
              type="text" 
              class="form-control" 
              name="keyFeature2" 
              placeholder="Provide the second key feature"  value="<%= clientData[0].keyFeature2 %>"
              pattern="[A-Za-z0-9\s]{5,60}"
              title="About should be min length of 5 and max length of 70 with A-Za-z" required>
  <input 
              id="keyFeature3" 
              type="text" 
              class="form-control" 
              name="keyFeature3" 
              placeholder="Provide the third key feature"  value="<%= clientData[0].keyFeature3 %>"
              pattern="[A-Za-z0-9\s]{5,60}"
              title="About should be min length of 5 and max length of 70 with A-Za-z" required>

   <input 
              id="keyFeature4" 
              type="text" 
              class="form-control" 
              name="keyFeature4" 
              placeholder="Provide the fourth key feature"  value="<%= clientData[0].keyFeature4 %>"
              pattern="[A-Za-z0-9\s]{5,60}"
              title="About should be min length of 5 and max length of 70 with A-Za-z" required></p>

  <p>This is how the product works</p>
  <p> Product demo screen one
    <input type="file" class="btn btn-default btn-file col-xs-12" name="screen1" value="<%= clientData[0].screen1 %>" required >
   About the demo screen 
  <input id="screen1Text" type="text" 
              class="form-control" 
              name="screen1Text" 
              placeholder="About the screen"
              pattern="[A-Za-z0-9\s]{5,60}" value="<%= clientData[0].screen1Text %>"
              title="About should be min length of 5 and max length of 70 with A-Za-z0-9.*&:" required> </p>
  
  <p> Product demo screen two
    <input type="file" class="btn btn-default btn-file col-xs-12" name="screen2"  value="<%= clientData[0].screen2 %>" required >
   About the demo screen two
  <input id="screen2Text" type="text" 
              class="form-control" 
              name="screen2Text" 
              placeholder="About the screen"
              pattern="[A-Za-z0-9\s]{5,60}" value="<%= clientData[0].screen2Text %>"
              title="About should be min length of 5 and max length of 70 with A-Za-z0-9.*&:" required> </p>
    
    <p> Product demo screen three
    <input type="file" class="btn btn-default btn-file col-xs-12" name="screen3" value="<%= clientData[0].screen3 %>" required >
   About the demo screen three
  <input id="screen3Text" type="text" 
              class="form-control" 
              name="screen3Text" 
              placeholder="About the screen" value="<%= clientData[0].screen3Text %>" 
              pattern="[A-Za-z0-9\s]{5,60}"
              title="About should be min length of 5 and max length of 70 with A-Za-z0-9.*&:" required> </p>
  
  <p> Adding to that now, He could also have</p>
  
   <input 
              id="benefit1" 
              type="text" 
              class="form-control" 
              name="benefit1" 
              placeholder="Provide your first benefit" 
              pattern="[A-Za-z0-9\s]{5,60}"  value="<%= clientData[0].benefit1 %>"
              title="About should be min length of 5 and max length of 70 with A-Za-z0-9.*&:" required>
   <input 
              id="benefit2" 
              type="text" 
              class="form-control" 
              name="benefit2" 
              placeholder="Provide your second benefit"
              pattern="[A-Za-z0-9\s]{5,60}"  value="<%= clientData[0].benefit2 %>"
              title="About should be min length of 5 and max length of 70 with A-Za-z0-9.*&:" required>
   <input 
              id="benefit3" 
              type="text" 
              class="form-control" 
              name="benefit3" 
              placeholder="Provide your third benefit"
              pattern="[A-Za-z0-9\s]{5,60}"  value="<%= clientData[0].benefit3 %>"
              title="About should be min length of 5 and max length of 70 with A-Za-z0-9.*&:" required>
  <p>Want to know more <input 
              id="contactDetails" 
              type="text" 
              class="form-control" 
              name="contactDetails" 
              placeholder="Add your contact details" value="<%= clientData[0].contactDetails %>"> </p>
                  <div align="center"> 
    <button type="submit">
      <svg version="1.1" class="send-icn" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" x="0px" y="0px" width="100px" height="36px" viewBox="0 0 100 36" enable-background="new 0 0 100 36" xml:space="preserve">
        <path d="M100,0L100,0 M23.8,7.1L100,0L40.9,36l-4.7-7.5L22,34.8l-4-11L0,30.5L16.4,8.7l5.4,15L23,7L23.8,7.1z M16.8,20.4l-1.5-4.3
  l-5.1,6.7L16.8,20.4z M34.4,25.4l-8.1-13.1L25,29.6L34.4,25.4z M35.2,13.2l8.1,13.1L70,9.9L35.2,13.2z" />
      </svg>
      <small>send</small>
    </button>
    </div>
  </p>
</form>
</div>

  <script src='http://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.1.3/jquery.min.js'></script>

    <script src="../../js/index.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
